class hello //class name oop concept
{
    public static void main(String args[]) //this is main function which is executed first
    {
        System.out.println("Hello World"); //print statement
    }
}


/* 
the above code is sent to "JAVA COMPILER",  this java compiler convert above code into "BYTE CODE"
then that byte code is sent to "JVM" (Java virtual Machine), byte code can be read only by JVM
this JVM converts byte code into Machine readable code 
then it is execute line by line and show output as "Hello World"
*/
